description: Try our easy to follow Prawns with Tartare Sauce recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Prawn dishes,Pescatarian,Prawn,Soy free,Tree nut free,Sesame free,Summer,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Prawns with Tartare Sauce Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 3kg extra large Australian Tiger Prawns (extra large)

recipeInstructions.text: We select only the best Australian Farmed Aussie Tiger Prawns from the northern coast of NSW and north Queensland to supply our customers with the freshest Australian seafood. This year we have the tastiest medium to jumbo-sized prawns to suit families of all sizes. For a simple, but special starter, serve with tatare sauce or aioli.
